snippet.textDisplay:
So I'm gonna be honest with y'all... I was never a big fan of TVXQ... It's not that I don't like, I just don't listen to it very often. I didn't even know who Max was until now. I discovered this song while randomly looking for kpop songs on Spotify. And I saw his album there. I was curious so I clicked on the first song, and now I'm addicted to it. Damn his voice is so unique! I think I never heard anything like it. It's amazing.
I was so amazed by his voice that I searched for him on YouTube and here I am. Learning that his name is Changmin and that he's a member of TVXQ.
Guys... His amazing. Unique voice, he's so handsome, and his dancing skills are on point. And of course I'll follow his solo career too
